Catalog of files and programs in this directory
-----------------------------------------------

Note: the .cc extension of executable c++ programs is in parentheses, because
you should leave out the .cc when you invoke the program.

File name             Programmer  Description
---------             ----------  -----------

alignment-stats.pl            EJ  Alignment statistics to diagnose misaligned corpora.
all-best-rr-vals              GF  Summarize a set of COW experiments.
